txt.en: You have defeated many Uruks upon Pelennor Fields.
You have defeated many Uruks upon Pelennor Fields before the coming battle.
Uruks can be found found patrolling Pelennor Fields.\n\nYou should defeat Uruks before the coming battle.

'Brutal Uruk-hai from the Morgul Vale stalk the fields. We must defeat these strong foes before those at Minas Tirith encounter them in battle. I fear most men would be torn apart by these vicious beasts.'
Uruk-hai from the Morgul Vale patrol Pelennor Fields. These strong foes should be defeated before the coming battle.
